{"tid":1023602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那條款！歐盟500:49立法通過嚴審「政治意圖的外資」","createTime":"2019-02-16T02:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T01:26:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00a02252cc2a6e5ffdf804dae25d628f6a1f5d00","tid":1023602,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"世界各國紛紛著手防止資訊、重要技術遭中國竊取，歐盟也不例外，歐洲議會今天壓倒性表決通過，嚴加審視來自境外的投資、收購，尤其是來自中國的資金。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，歐洲議會今天以500票同意、49票反對、56票棄權，通過立法嚴加審查境外對「戰略行業」的投資與收購，包含水資源、交通、通訊、半導體、人工智慧、航太、媒體產業等等。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會議員普魯斯特（Franck Proust）說，嚴加審視不是為了禁止外國投資，而是要「注意一些奇怪的投資，那些不是為了經濟、而是為了政治的投資」。<br />\n<br />\n儘管歐盟執委會（European Commission）之前曾特別就資安問題警告中國，歐盟貿易專員仍澄清，這項立法是中立、不帶歧視的。"},{"pid":"16dd6c64dd6355094a30d6a86fdaa7011f655af1","tid":1023602,"uid":25858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"全球圍堵行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aebed66ae0a2c03870482399dedd0ecae9f0680","tid":1023602,"uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"誠哥一早買哂，<br />\n<br />\n支那又要跪低向誠哥求救"},{"pid":"5e3f66c343954a3c2a8595b06bf890b18f3365fc","tid":1023602,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"1038無嘢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a1b2ac0eb5464fa9a51b31038db19e5500eee0","tid":1023602,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"49票反對係乜撚野國家黎架？"},{"pid":"3a8ec856f4ec1973147c6e4c37d95fc50a004b39","tid":1023602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5280f1188c7cc38df7e405cabb095245